window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Carwyn ap Bryn and Brigid Connor are two elemental vampires finding the lost, righting wrongs, and searching for meaning in the endless stretch of immortality they’ve been granted.</p> <p>And trying not to blow things up, but that might be more aspirational.</p> <p>Everyone said that Lupe Martínez was a good kid. She listened to her mom, she helped at the homeless shelter, she got good grades, and she had a bright future ahead of her.</p> <p>Until she disappeared.</p> <p>Now no one knows what to think. The police are sure she ran away; her mother is sure she didn’t. Days have passed and no one knows what to do until her family priest suggests they call in an old friend.</p> <p>A <i>very</i> old friend.</p> <p><i>Saint’s Passage</i> is the first book in the paranormal mystery series Elemental Covenant by Elizabeth Hunter, <i>USA Today</i> best-selling author of the Elemental Legacy series, the Glimmer Lake Series, and the Irin Chronicles.</p>"; 
